## List
다양한 데이터 타입을 담을 수 있는 데이터 타입



::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
list1 <- list(1, 2, 3, 4, '5')
list1[[5]]
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}

```
[1] "5"
```


:::

```{.r .cell-code}
names(list1) <- c('a', 'b', 'c', 'd', 'e')
```
:::



## dataframe



::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
df <- data.frame(a = 1:5, b = c('a', 'b', 'c', 'd', 'e'))
df$a
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}

```
[1] 1 2 3 4 5
```


:::

```{.r .cell-code}
df$b
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}

```
[1] "a" "b" "c" "d" "e"
```


:::
:::
